A man, 34, was arrested after being caught driving a stolen vehicle on the N2 near Humansdorp yesterday. The white VW Polo with a CA registration number was spotted after police were alerted by a private tracking company about 11.30am yesterday. Police confirmed that the car had been stolen during a weekend house robbery in Motherwell. The man will appear in the Humansdorp Magistrate s Court today. Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share